::KitKat::

She looked at Stringtra.
"HE'S UNDER WATER?!"  She dove into the water in beast mode and swam 
as far she she could looking for Quickstrike.  She touched rocks and 
soil on the sides of the pool walls.  Something brushed against her 
leg and she swam away from it.  She had to return to the surface for 
air. "I CAN"T FIND HIM!"
She dove down again.
